snippet.title: BULLCRAP: Final Trailer
snippet.description: It's almost here! This is the final trailer for BULLCRAP! A game of Lies, Poop and Deceit! See loadeddeckgames.com for the latest news. Coming soon to Steam! New cross-platform Multiplayer version to be released on iOS and Android soon!
